title: Moonfall Movie Review
summary: My thoughts on the movie Moonfall. Spolier its meh.

body.raw:
I have alot of time on my hands and so I watch random movies like Moonfall. Especially if its Sci-fi or fantsay I will watch
it no matter the reviews. I noticed it has the Game of Thrones guy John Bradley which I kind of liked his character in GOT.
I would say John did a good job of his role in Moonfall as well. The rest of the movie to me is just one of those "2012" type
movies where everything is falling apart and shit is flying every where, including helicopters that can fly through a giant wave
of water with zero problems...

So that would all make sense seeing how the director is Roland Emmerich which also did 2012, The Day After Tomorrow, etc.

![Test](/static/images/blog2023/test_2of5.png)
